          "from_upn": null,
          "sent_utc": "2026-06-15T12:36:34.196Z",
          "sent_mt": "2026-06-15T06:36:34-06:00",
          "text": "A combination of things. I held the chocolate up while verifying the status of the caramel. Once it was verified, we only have 1 warehouse person splitting time between 2 buildings on the busiest day at the busiest time every Monday and he gets pulled both directions continuously. So the caramel and chocolate were delayed. In the meantime, room temperature caramel was loaded into the tank and we had to wait for it to reach an acceptable temp, which was sped up by adding some of the warm caramel when it was pulled.",
